spec_data.Name: perl-Log-Any-IfLOG
spec_data.Description:
This module is a drop-in replacement/wrapper for Log::Any to be used from
your modules. This is a quick-hack solution to avoid the cost of loading
Log::Any under "normal condition".
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 12:52:04 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Load Log::Any only if "logging is enabled"
